\[\overrightarrow{\mathbf{ap}} \cdot \overrightarrow{\mathbf{ac}} = (\mathbf{p} - \mathbf{a}) \cdot (\mathbf{c} - \mathbf{a}) = 0.\]This gives us the system of equations
\begin{align*}
